dcterms:description: The Multi-Object Video (MOVi) dataset consists of synthetic video sequences designed for evaluating object-centric learning models. It includes various categories of scenes with different complexities, featuring multiple objects and varying backgrounds.
dcterms:title: Multi-Object Video (MOVi)
